rows.label: tlk45320159_05_msg0001
rows.name:
As far as our Imperial Army duties
here go, there's been nothing out
of the ordinary.

rows.label: tlk45320159_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I hear things have been pretty hectic
down at Port Anangham, though.

rows.label: tlk45320159_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Only things trying to get into the
capital from this side have been
the usual monsters.

rows.label: tlk45320159_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Funny how violent monsters that can't
be reasoned with are actually the easier
threat to be facing nowadays.
